<description>

The Submissions view presents a table of all student submission records. Search and filter controls above the table allow narrowing by student name, submission status, and grading status. The table columns are: Student identity (name and initials icon, links to profile), Submission status (e.g., Submitted for grading, No submission, Draft — not submitted), Grading status (e.g., Graded, Not graded), Submission date/time, Time since submission, Online text preview, File submission links, Submission comments, Feedback comments, Feedback files, and Final grade. Each row has an action menu to open the grading workflow for that student. A "Quick grading" mode can be enabled to allow inline grade entry directly in the table.

---



</description>

<workflows>
WF-001 | Search by student name | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Student_Search | on_success: Table is filtered to match the student search query, narrowing visible submissions.
WF-002 | Filter by submission status | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Submission_Status_Filter | on_success: Table is filtered by the selected Submission Status (e.g., Submitted for grading, No submission, Draft — not submitted).
WF-003 | Filter by grading status | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Grading_Status_Filter | on_success: Table is filtered by the selected Grading Status (Graded or Not graded).
WF-004 | Enable Quick Grading mode | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Quick_Grading_Mode | on_success: Quick Grading Mode enabled; inline grade entry (Final_Grade) becomes editable directly in the table.
WF-005 | Open student profile from row | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Student_Identity | on_success: Link opens the student's profile.
WF-006 | Open online text preview | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Online_Text_Preview | on_success: Opens an inline preview of the student's online text submission.
WF-007 | Open submitted files | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: File_Submissions | on_success: Links to submitted files are opened for download or viewing.
WF-008 | Open submission comments | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Submission_Comments | on_success: Opens the submission comments thread or modal.
WF-009 | Open or add feedback comments | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Feedback_Comments | on_success: Opens or allows adding feedback comments for the submission.
WF-010 | Open feedback files | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Feedback_Files | on_success: Links to feedback files are opened for download or viewing.
WF-011 | Open grading workflow for a student | actor: teacher or grader | branch: none | terminal: Open Grading Workflow | on_success: Opens the grading workflow for the selected student.
WF-012 | Edit final grade inline (Quick Grading enabled) | actor: teacher or grader | branch: Quick_Grading_Mode == true | terminal: Final_Grade | on_success: Final grade is edited inline in the table when Quick Grading Mode is enabled.
</workflows>

